social_posts.post_text:
Shout out to @thebiscuit.bar and @boardwalkgranitepark for having me out this week for SUCH a great meal! Absolutely LOVED strolling along the boardwalk and enjoying a great meal! 

Happy Wednesday foodies!

I cannot believe that I haven’t been to @gloriaslatincuisine SOONER!!! Visited Gloria’s for the first time and fell in love with the atmosphere and their incredible food! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
⭐️ Ceviche Trio: sampler of orange roughy ceviche, aguachile and shrimp cocktail 
⭐️ Chicken & Beef fajitas 

I can’t wait to go back!! 

@gloriaslatincuisine 📍 3635 W University Drive, McKinney, TX 75071

@soulbirdchicken is NOW OPEN at @thehilldallas 🎉 

Looking for some crispy chicken that is cooked to perfection?!! @soulbirdchicken is your place! This new location is at 8031 Walnut Hl Ln #1150
Dallas, TX 75231!! 

If you visit within the first month from when they open their chkn coop doors & sign up for their rewards program, you will be entered into a raffle to win one of the following:

🍗 50” Samsung Flatscreen TV
🍗 FREE Soul Bird for a YEAR!
🍗 $100 gift card
🍗 $50 gift card

So go check them out and win some awesome prizes YALL!!!!

SAVE THIS REEL AND GO CHECK OUT @lasupremamarket IN FRISCO, TX!!! Not only do the kindest people work here, but they also have just about everything you need! They have a FRESH meat market, groceries, fresh veggies, and also an INCREDIBLE kitchen where you can order some tasty food!! 

@lasupremamarket also has a book drive going on right now!! Go donate your books 📚 @dallasbooktribe would be SO GRATEFUL! 🤩🎉

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🌮 Quesabirria Tacos (MY FAVORITE!!!) 
🌮 HOMEMADE TAMALES!! (you can preorder by the dozen @ $19.99) 
🌮 Shrimp Cocktail (YUM!!!) 
🌮 Taco Plate 

They also offer a happy hour M-F from 5-7 PM on their taco plate 🥰 the taco plate is $11 WITH a free 16 oz drink. SIGN ME UP!!! 

Also shout out to the legend who made this INCREDIBLE food, @edsel1406 🎉🎉

@verfstavern in Flower Mound, TX has a KILLER brunch! $3 dollar mimosas and a fabulous brunch selection?!? Sign me up!! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🥑 Avocado Toast: Pecan crusted toast topped with fresh smashed avocado, toasted pepitas and chopped candied bacon, drizzled with maple glaze.
🥑 pecan crusted French broad toast: Served with bacon and Vermont Maple syrup.

Happy Saturday y’all!

WHO IS READY FOR CHRISTMAS?!? 

Y’all I don’t visit Fort Worth as much as I would like to! This city is full of so many fun and exciting places and I NEED to explore these spots more often. 

Found a few awesome places that I wanted to share with y’all to get in the Christmas spirit! 

Wandering Foodie Fort Worth Fav: 
⭐️ @thedustybiscuit has THE BEST beignets EVERRR! I tried the brown butter, sugar plum, and cowtown king cake! 
⭐️ @wintonandwaits is the cutest boutique! They have a variety of cute Christmas items, clothes, and other adorable things for your home! 
⭐️ @nickelcityfwtx is the Christmas bar of ALL Christmas bars!!! They are decked out in holiday decorations! They also have some fabulous Christmas drinks as well. 

Where is your favorite place to go in @visitfortworth

@pjscoffee HOLIDAY DRINKS ARE BAAAAACK!!!! 

Pj’s coffee has some YUMMY new holiday specialty flavors. I stopped by the @pjscoffeeeuless location and tried their coffee flight! Have you ever had a coffee flight before?! IT. IS. AWESOME! 

Wandering Foodie Coffee Favs: 
☕️ Peppermint Bark Latte 
☕️ Butter Rum Latte 
☕️ Cookie Dough Oat Milk Latte
☕️Jingle Bells Latte 
☕️ Beignets! (So good!) 

My personal favorite was the cookie dough oat milk latte! 🥛 

Which flavor would you try first?!?

The holidays are QUICKLY approaching so I have partnered with @lasupremamarket in Frisco, TX for a fabulous giveaway! Check out the details below on how to win $100 to their market!!! 

How to Enter:
1. Follow @lasupremamarket @wandering_foodie_  and @pr_blend 
2. Like this reel
3. Tag a friend you want to go shopping with (unlimited entries!) 
4. Share this reel to your story and tag us for an additional five entries! 

This is for their market, which includes groceries, meats, veggies, etc! So much to choose from! The winner will be announced this Friday, December 16! GOOD LUCK!

I felt like I was transported to New Orleans when I took a bite out of these beignets! 

@thedustybiscuit is INCREDIBLE!!!! Their beignets are fluffy, flavorful and just overall DELICIOUS! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
⭐️ Brown Butter 
⭐️ Sugar Plum 
⭐️ Cowtown King Cake 

Have you ever had a beignet before?!

I LOVE @drivemegrazeyboards 🤩😍

She makes the most extravagant and stunning charcuterie boards!!! If you’re planning on having a girls night or a party, ORDER A CHARCUTERIE BOARD FROM HER!!! I was absolutely blown away by this masterpiece!!!! 

Thank you @drivemegrazeyboards for this spectacular board!!

Family fondue!!!!! 

With the holidays coming up, this is the PERFECT way to celebrate with friends and family!

My husband, @stationary_foodie_ and I hosted a fondue night and had cheese and dessert fondue and it was an absolute BLAST!!!! 

Have you ever tried fondue?!!!

I’m BACK with an AWESOME spot in Plano, TX y’all!!!! @rickyshotchicken is WHERE IT’S AT!!!! This is DFW’s spot for Nashville Hot Chicken. 

Also not going to lie, as I made this reel it made me hungry all over again and crave their chicken sandwich!!! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🐔 Quarter Bird with fries 
🐔 The Sando: Buttered Bun, Breast, Vinegar Slaw, Comeback Sauce, Pickles (served with fries and a drink!!) 
🐔 Fireballs (ORDER THESE Y’ALL!!!!!!!) 
🐔 Banana Pudding 

Another awesome thing about @rickyshotchicken is that you get to choose your spice level. I chose mild and it was light on the heat which was perfect! 

They also have locations in Richardson and Arlington! 

Have a great week foodies!

ALWAYS in the mood for Brunch! (Especially when it’s at @winewoodgrill ) 

Enjoyed an absolutely fabulous meal from the SPECTACULAR, @winewoodgrill in Grapevine, TX! 
They are located on Main Street!

This restaurant is seriously the best! They had live music playing today, they have an awesome menu selection, and the coffee gave me LIFE!!! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🍳 Winewood Hash: tenderloin filet with potatoes, arugula, asparagus, and tomatoes tossed in a creamy horseradish sauce (topped with 2 sunny side up eggs) 
🍳 Croque Madame: black forest ham and swiss cheese on toasted brioche, topped with smoked gouda and a sunny side up egg 
🍳 Biscuits and Sausage Gravy: four housemate biscuits topped with sausage gravy 
🍳 BlackBerry Bramble 
🍳 Cold Brew Old Fashioned 

What would you dive into first??!!

I could eat pizza for every meal 🤩 🍕 

@urbancrust has one of my favorite pizzas of all time! They are located in Downtown Plano! 

Highly recommend the Buffalina: 12 in. pizza crust baked and topped with marinated teardrop tomatoes fresh buffalo mozzarella, basil, garlic, virgin olive oil, shaved grana padano cheese

What are your favorite pizza toppings?!?!

Looking for an elegant restaurant in the heart of Plano?

Craving seafood? Craving steak? @flemingssteakhouse has it ALLLLL!! 

My family visited Fleming’s in Plano last weekend and it was a top notch experience! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🦞 North Atlantic Lobster Tails 
🦞 Prime New York Strip
🦞 Crème Brûlée 
🦞 Chocolate Gooey Butter Cake 

#notsponsored just some REALLY good food!!

🌟 SNEAK PEEK 🌟 into the ALL NEW @thetoastedyolk in Addison, TX!!! (stay tuned for their grand opening!) 

The Toasted Yolk offers ALL DAY BREAKFAST (what more could you ask for??!!). Not only do they have breakfast, but they’ve also got Bellinis, bloody Mary’s and Mimosas! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🥞 Buttermilk Pancakes with Strawberries 
🥞 Cowboy Scrambler: Two buttermilk biscuits, with bacon, sausage, ham, onions, and three scrambled eggs topped with country sausage gravy. 
🥞 Avocado Toast: Grilled artisan bread topped with avocado, pico de gallo, and two eggs cooked to order. Served with mixed greens dressed with Lemon Za’atar Vinaigrette. (I ordered my eggs over easy and on the side!) 
🥞 Bellini: Sparkling wine, peach nectar, and Triple Sec. Served frozen!!!

What is your go to breakfast meal?!

Strawberry Pancakes with Whipped Cream and Butter! Perfect brunch meal 🍓 🥞 

@thetoastedyolk

You KNOW you want a piece of this pizza!!! 

@napolis_east_plano hit it out of the park yet again with their delicious supreme pizza. My thoughts on pizza: the more toppings, THE BETTER!!!! 

So cheesy, so delicious 🍕 

What are your favorite pizza toppings?

All of the Texas Food Groups: ribs, Turkey, brisket, and TEXAS TWINKIES!! @hutchins_bbq has some of the BEST BBQ IN TEXAS Y’ALL!!!!! 

I visited @hutchins_bbq McKinney, TX location and was BLOWN AWAY by the quality of the food and the FRIENDLINESS of the staff. Hutchins feels like my home away from home 🏡 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🍖 Brisket 
🍖 Jalapeño Cheddar Smoked Sausage 
🍖 Pork Ribs 
🍖 Smoked Turkey Breast 
🍖 Chicken 
🍖 TEXAS TWINKIES: jalapeño stuffed with brisket & cream cheese and wrapped in premium thick cut bacon
🍖 Peach Cobbler and Banana Pudding 

Make sure to check out their McKinney location at 1301 N Tennessee Street OR their Frisco location at 9225 Preston Rd 😍😍

Nacho toppings piled high to the sky! 

Recently I have been craving chips and salsa and also nachos!!! This treat is always on my mind! Thank you to @cristinasfinemex for satisfying my craving!!!! 

I visited @cristinasfinemex over in McKinney, TX located at 2811 Craig Dr STE 110, McKinney, TX 75070! 

Wandering Foodie Fav: 
🧀 Tex-Mex Nachos: warm chips topped with refried beans, chile con queso, seasoned taco meat, pickled jalapenos, shredded lettuce, pico de gallo, sour cream & chopped cilantro

Sooooo many flavorful toppings made this the perfect meal!!!

This French toast is doing the most 😍

The Hydeout Cafe is one of my favorite local breakfast spots in McKinney! They always have freshly brewed coffee and of course TASTY food!!! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🥞 Very Berry French Toast: French toast topped with strawberries, blackberries, blueberries and raspberries with powdered sugar 

Are you more of a French toast or pancake fan?!?

❗️CAFE GECKO IN FAIRVIEW❗️

This AWESOME spot in Fairview, TX offers a scratch kitchen and they are open LATE!! Great vibes, fantastic food, and DELICIOUS cocktails!!! @cafegeckofairview 

While you’re here, you have GOT to order their pizza with white sauce (10/10 pizza AND the cheese pull was ON POINT!!!) 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
⭐️ Queso & Chips 
⭐️ Stuffed Jalapeños 
⭐️ Shrimp Cocktail 
⭐️ Steak and Cheese Sandwich 
⭐️ Pizza with white sauce 
⭐️ Mexican Candy Cocktail 

LOCATION: 239 Town Pl, Fairview, TX 75069

What dish would you dive into first?!??

Let me introduce you to @flemingssteakhouse 🥩 

This beautiful steakhouse is located in Plano, Texas and they offer a WONDERFUL variety of steaks, seafood, and desserts. This spot is elegant & classy 💫 

I have SUCH a sweet-tooth so I immediately dug into that cheesecake! And don’t forget to try their STUNNING seafood tower (not only is it pretty to look at, but it’s also delicious!!) 

Located at: 7250 Dallas Pkwy Suite 110, Plano, TX 75024

BIG thank you to @visitplano for having me out!!!! ❤️❤️❤️

These are a few of my favorite things 🎶 

Sharing some of my favorite shots from my visit with @cafegeckofairview in Fairview, TX! Awesome food, the friendliest service, and just an overall spectacular time! 

GO CHECK THEM OUT Y’ALL!

THE BEST LOCALLY OWNED PIZZERIA IN FRISCO, TX!!! Everyone, I introduce to you @halo_pizzeria_tx 🍕 

Halo Pizzeria is truly one of a kind. They make everything in house, including their pizza, sauces, their RANCH (and y’all…. That ranch is SO GOOD!!) they also offer local, hand crafted sodas with all natural ingredients!! 

The coolest of all: all of the owners are local! (And also probably some of the kindest people you’ll ever meet). 

WHILE YOU ARE HERE, GET THE J PIE!!!!! Best dessert pizza EVERRRR! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🍕 Garlic Knots 
🍕 Buffalo Wings 
🍕 The Heritage Pizza: Pomodoro tomato sauce, mozzarella, seasonal market veggies (roasted peppers, caramelized onions, roasted cherry tomatoes, mushrooms, spinach) ADDED SAUSAGE 
🍕 The Sem: Garlic butter base, mozzarella, prosciutto, fig jelly, balsamic glaze, arugula 
🍕 The J Pie: Mascarpone, cookie butter, Nutella, house made sugar cookies, cinnamon, nutmeg

Which pie would you try first?!?!
Pizza, wings, and garlic knots. You can’t go wrong with this combo 😍 @halo_pizzeria_tx

GIVEAWAY CLOSED!!!!

$50 GIVEAWAY WITH @hatcreekburgers 🍔 (see details below!!) 

In honor of @hatcreekburgers 15th birthday in September, they will be offering FREE 9 oz. Birthday Shakes to guests who place an order of $10 or more anytime between Sept. 1-4 (Labor Day weekend). 😍😍

Not only that, I’ve got more exciting news because you can also win a $50 gift card to @hatcreekburgers 🍔 

Here are the rules: 
1. Follow @hatcreekburgers and @wandering_foodie_ 
2. Like this post 
3. Tag a friend you’d share these burgers and shakes with (unlimited entries!!!) 

WINNER WILL BE ANNOUNCED ON TUESDAY, SEPTEMBER 5!!! 

***this giveaway is not affiliated or endorsed by Instagram!*** winner will be DM’d by ME directly!

BBQ tastes even BETTER on Labor Day 🍗 

@lockhartsmokehouse in downtown Plano has some mouthwatering bbq!!! They also have locations in Dallas’ Bishop Arts District and Texas Live! in Arlington!!! 

We tried a variety of meats and sides and everything was SOOOO GOOD! I fell in LOVE with that Mac and cheese. And while you’re there, you HAVE to order their Bloody Mary (IT IS EPIC!!!) 

What are you doing this Labor Day?!

Taco Bout a TASTY MEAL! @bigtacoandseafood is located in McKinney, TX and they have some MOUTHWATERING FOOD! 

Whether you’re craving nachos, salads, fajitas, or seafood, they’ve got it all and they have an awesome selection to choose from. 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
💃🏼 Parrillada: chicken, steak & shrimp fajitas with melted cheese, grilled onions and peppers 
💃🏼 Pork and Pineapple Nachos: 6 crispy tortilla halves with meat and melted cheese along with beans and cheese 

There are soooo many more items on the menu I want to try next!!! 

@bigtacoandseafood is located at 1620 N Hardin Blvd, McKinney, TX 75071!!!

Best coffee shop in Kansas City @messengercoffee ☕️ 

One of my favorite things to do OF ALL TIME is finding new coffee shops in new cities. I was in Kansas City last weekend for my best friend’s wedding and stopped by Messenger Coffee. THIS PLACE WAS AWESOME!!!! 

They had a variety of baked goods (my favorite was the pumpkin muffin!) 

FOODIE FRIENDS: where is your favorite coffee shop of ALL TIME?! Where should I visit next?!?!

Instagram VS Reality 😂😂 Happy 1st birthday to my sweet Bobby!!! 🐶 

The sweetest little Boykin Spaniel in the world 🌍 and @stationary_foodie_ & I are so lucky!! Bobby is FULL of energy, always has a smile on his face, and is such a cuddly boy. 

His day has been full of toys and treats!!

The best fried green tomatoes around! And they can be found right in @downtownmckinney at @harvestmckinney 😍😍😍

Impromptu date night with @stationary_foodie_ at Harvest and it was SOOOO good! I always love checking out their menu and seeing what’s new. 

These fried green tomatoes include: cornmeal crusted tomatoes / fresh tomatoes / peaches / lemon ricotta / basil-peach pesto / micro basil 🌿 

Y’all, the peaches were the PERFECT addition!!!! 

Would you try this appetizer?!?!

Pineapples + pork = a sweet and salty combination your need with our nachos 😋

📸: @wandering_foodie_ 

#bigtacoandseafood #mckinneytx #nachos #mckinneyfood  #authenticmexicanfood #pineaaple

The best manicotti in Nashville! @eatavo  offers a wide variety of plant based dishes. 

Their food is FLAVORFUL, fresh, and savory! The manicotti consisted of Lemon herb almond ricotta, arrabiatta, parmesan cream! We also tried the Lentil Walnut burger which included Lentil-walnut patty, lettuce, tomato, onion, beet ketchup, chickpea mayo, sweet potato bun (I ordered without the ketchup) and it was DELICIOUS!!! 

I wish that they had a Dallas location!!! 

What is your favorite plant based meal?

Some of my favorite moments in Nashville 🤠❤️

Ate a LOT of good food, spent time with my incredible family, and got to explore a new city.

A meal for every day of the week! 🍝 

MARK YOUR CALENDARS FOR OCTOBER 14!!!! @doughbrosdallas will be having their GRAND OPENING in Plano, TX!! There will be door prizes, live music, and it will be full of fun!! 🎉 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🍝 Pepperoni Rolls 
🍝 Bruschetta 
🍝 The Bro Pizza (Marinara, pepperoni, ham, bacon, sausage, mozzarella & parmesan mix) 
🍝 Baked Ziti (MY FAVORITE!!!) 
🍝 Spaghetti & Meatballs 
🍝 Cannoli and Tiramisu 

Which dish would you try first?!

A batch made in heaven! 🍪 

These cookies were made with love by @cookiedelishfrisco out of Frisco, TX!!! These are some of FRESHEST cookies that I’ve had the pleasure of eating! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🍪 Reese's Pieces Peanut Butter
🍪 Chocolate Chip 
🍪 Chocolate Chip Pecan Sandie
🍪 M&M Chocolate Chip 
🍪 Sprinklers 
🍪 Strawberry White Chocolate Chip (MY FAVORITE!!!!!) 
🍪 Oatmeal Cream Pie 

@cookiedelishfrisco delivers to Frisco, Little Elm, Prosper and more!! 

Which flavor would you try first??

MY FAVORITE PLACE TO GET PASTRIES!!!!! @therosemarybakery in McKinney, TX has THE BEST pastries!!! I look forward to stopping by @mckinneyfarmersmarket every Saturday to pick up these sweet treats! 

Pictured is their Apple Strudel (and it was INCREDIBLE!!!!!) 

@therosemarybakery is at the McKinney Farmer’s Market every Saturday! You can also pre-order online and pick it up that Saturday!! 

Their menu goes live EVERY SUNDAY at 6 PM!!!! So go check them out!!!! 

https://therosemarybakery.com

Calling all of my tiramisu lovers!!! @doughbrosdallas has some TASTY tiramisu! Their desserts are sure to satisfy ANY sweet tooth’s cravings 😍

What is your favorite dessert???

Nothing wrong with diving into dessert first! 

Enjoyed a MAGICAL evening at @citylinedfw in Richardson, TX where I dined at @tricky_fish_ 🐠

@citylinedfw brings DELIGHTFUL restaurant options and entertainment right into the heart of Richardson. They host several fun events (check out their website: https://citylinedfw.com)

When you’re visiting, make sure to stop by @tricky_fish_ !! They have delicious options on their menu. I loved their boudin balls and also their French Toast Sundae. You have GOT to try the margarita flight too!!!!

Have you ever tried boudin balls before?! I had NEVER heard of them until I met @stationary_foodie_ ❤️ now whenever I see these tasty treats on a menu, I HAVE to order them!! 

@tricky_fish_ in @citylinedfw offers some DELICIOUS boudin balls. And that dipping sauce was great!!! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🐠 Boudin Balls (service with Piquant sauce) 
🐠 Raspberry Smash: raspberry infused @nuevodka with lime, thyme, & peach bitters 
🐠 Margarita Flight 

Have you ever tried boudin balls before?!

THE STATE FAIR OF TEXAS IS HERE!!! And I’ve got ALLLLL the best food recommendations for you to try!! Now I had to get a little messy to eat these delicious foods, but I was up for the job! 😛

***SAVE THIS REEL FOR WHEN YOU GO TO THE FAIR!!

Foods that I tried (IN ORDER OF THE VIDEO!!) 
🎪 @fletcherscornydogs (they have six different flavors to try y’all!!!!!) my favorite was the jalapeño & cheese corny dog! 
🎪 @stifflersconcessions The Sirloin Steak Bowl was SOOOO DELICIOUS! 
🎪 @chefcassy Peanut Butter and Jelly Wings (FANTASTIC! Loved the crunch!) 
🎪 @nevinsconcessions Fried Charcuterie Board and Peach Bellini! (GET THE FRIED CHARCUTERIE Y’ALL!) 
🎪 @chef_abel Fried PB&Js and fried cookie dough (I was OBSESSED with their fried PB&J with strawberry!) 
🎪 @jacksfrenchfrys loved these fries! Don’t forget to add vinegar and salt! 
🎪 @ferniesfunnelcakes and @ferniesfunnelcakecream I love their original funnel cake. And you HAVE to try the funnel cake cream cookie shot!!! (21+ ONLY for the cookie shot!!) 
🎪 @smokeyjohnsbbq that TURKEY LEG BLEW ME AWAY! First time trying a Turkey leg and it was AWESOME!!! 

And Of course, had to feature the one AND ONLY, BIG TEX!!!!!! 

Are you going to the @statefairoftx this year?!?

Would you try a fried Charcuterie board?! 

I had the PLEASURE of trying this flavorful fried charcuterie board made by the ONE AND ONLY @nevinsconcessions 😍😍😍 

Let me tell y’all…. If you’re going to the @statefairoftx you HAVE to add this to your list of foods to try!!!!

Where are my PB&J lovers at?!?? 

Y’all I’ve got another great @statefairoftx FAN FAV food for you! Make sure to visit @chef_abel at the State Fair and try the FRIED PB&J AND the fried cookie dough!!!! 

Would you try fried PB&J?!??

Sirloin Steak Bowl from @statefairoftx 😍😍😍 made by @stifflersconcessions 🎉 

🎟️ 22 Coupons 🎟️

Delicious steak with peppers and MASHED POTATOES 😍😍

Mom & Dad ❤️ 

Thank you so much @amanda.raylee for capturing these amazing moments!!!! So excited to meet baby Mitchell next month!!! 👦

Take me back to @rubysunshinebrunch in Nashville, TN! 

Ruby Sunshine offers a FANTASTIC brunch! I stopped by when I was in Nashville last month and LOVED IT!!! 

Next time you’re in Nashville, try out their Seasonal Stuffed French Toast (Brioche French toast stuffed with featured cheesecake filling) SIGN ME UPPPPP! 

What do you like to order at brunch?!

The loveliest lobster 🦞 

@texas_restaurant is one of my TOP favorite restaurants in all of DFW. They offer impeccable service, high quality food, with a fantastic atmosphere 😍

My personal favorite is their 8 oz Lobster Tail with their whipped potatoes & burnt corn! 

Texas Restaurant: 3609 Shire Boulevard Richardson, TX 75082

If a pizza has veggies on it, that makes it healthy right?! 😜 

Loooooved this pizza that I tried at @halo_pizzeria_tx 🍕 🥗 

The Sem: Garlic butter base, mozzarella, prosciutto, fig jelly, balsamic glaze, arugula

What are your favorite pizza toppings?!

DATE NIGHT at @cadillacpizza in @downtownmckinney 🍕 

First time trying their pizza and it was DELICIOUS! When it comes to pizza, the more toppings, the better! This supreme pizza hit the spot! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🍕 Original Supreme: red sauce / pepperoni / spicy sausage / ham / mushroom / black olive / onion / bell pepper / mozzarella
🍕 Fire Roasted Hummus & Pita Bread: roasted red peppers / feta / chipotle-infused olive oil

FANTASTIC experience!!!!

I’ve never met a charcuterie board that I didn’t like! 😋 

If you’re a charcuterie fan, you have GOT to check out @ten.one.artisanal in Denton, TX! They have an awesome cheese selection (cheeses from ALL around the world). And y’all…. Everything is made in house, FRESH, DAILY! 😍😍

Newest obsession!! 🧀

Perfect weather for some coffee & farmers markets!! 

Stopped by @yiayiascoffee over at the @friscofreshmkt in Frisco, TX! HAD to try their iced caramel macchiato and it was fantastic 😍😍 SO frothy & smooth! 

Enjoyed walking around the farmers market and checking out all of the awesome booths! 

Where is your favorite farmers market?! I have only been to the McKinney farmers market and Frisco farmers market. Always on the hunt for new ones to visit!

The ultimate Christmas store!!! 🤶 🎄 🎁 

Visited @holidaywarehouse in Plano, Texas and absolutely LOVED seeing ALL of the Christmas decorations. They had anything from Christmas trees, to Christmas ornaments, to decorations! It was SO fun exploring! 

Quite a few of the items were out of my budget but MAN was it fun looking around!!! 

@holidaywarehouse is located at 2819 W 15th St
Plano, TX  75075!!

One of my favorite breakfast spots of ALL time!!! @firstwatch consistently has tasty food and great service. 

I originally found them when I lived in Cincinnati and was SO EXCITED when they made their way down to TX! 

They have an awesome seasonal menu as well. I HIGHLY recommend the Steak and Bacon Breakfast Burrito on their seasonal menu. Full of flavor & it’ll leave you full and happy 😃

Welcome to the world, Wandering Baby 🍼👶🏼👩‍🍼 Sweet Jack made his debut on Tuesday, November 14 and we love him SOOOO much! ❤️❤️❤️

I can’t get over how cute and tiny his little fingers are 🥹

It felt SO nice getting out of the house today and exploring a local coffee shop! @armorcoffee in Allen, TX is a great local spot with some delicious coffee ☕️ 

I ordered their cookie butter latte and absolutely LOVED IT! (They also have their winter drinks out and available on the menu!) 

@armorcoffee is located at 190 E Stacy Rd #408, Allen, TX 75002

What coffee shop in DFW should I stop by next?!

Happy Thanksgiving Y’all!

I spent this thanksgiving with my family and we ate SOO much delicious food! Shout out to my sister in law for making an INCREDIBLE Turkey!!! 

P.S if you’ve never tried the pumpkin cheesecake from @cheesecakefactory you are MISSING OUT! 

What is your favorite thanksgiving food?!?!

Sunday mornings in Oklahoma 🌞 

Chilly morning with a warm cup of coffee in hand. With my favorite mug from @rebasplace ☕️ ❤️ 

Happy Sunday foodies!

Ventured out and found a new ADORABLE coffee shop in McKinney! @whiteboxroastery is located in @cottonmillartsdistrict and they have some fantastic coffee! 

I always love exploring & finding new coffee shops. I am SOOO happy that I stumbled upon this spot. I tried their cinnamon honey oat latte (SO GOOD!) and my husband tried the vanilla bean latte (also delicious!) 

This coffee shop is elevated while still cozy! I also love how it’s connected to @cottonmillartsdistrict 😍😍

Where should I visit next?!?!

My husband surprised me with @mr.tako001 for dinner! This was my first time trying Mr. Tako and y’all, their food is SOOO DELICIOUS!!! 

Today was a tough day! From dealing with our water claim and the damage to our house, to navigating life with a newborn! These tacos brought me SO MUCH HAPPINESS!! Thank you @stationary_foodie_ for this amazing treat! 

Wandering Foodie Favs: 
🌮 Al Pastor Tacos 
🌮 Asada Fries 
🌮 Chips and Salsa 

Mr. Tako is located in McKinney, TX at 1330 N McDonald St, McKinney, TX 75071!! 

Have you ever been to @mr.tako001 ?!?!

It’s the most wonderful time of the year 🎄especially when you have a Chip Cookie in your hand! 

Chip Cookies has an ALL NEW location in Plano, Texas! 

I loved stopping by to try some of their yummy cookies flavors. I also LOVED how I could customize my own toppings on my cookies!

I usually stick to posting about going out to eat, but recently I’ve been testing out some new recipes and cooking more! With a newborn at home, it’s harder to go out these days 🤣 This evening, I had the pleasure of cooking the FAMOUS Carlin Tortellini Soup (a speciality that my friend created!) 

This is perfect for the holidays and for Christmas and it feeds a lot of people! 

INGREDIENTS: 
1. 1 lb Italian Sausage 
2. 1 lb Pork Sausage 
3. 2 packages of cheese tortellini 
4. 1/2 Cup Dry Red Wine 
5. 1/2 Cup Water 
6. 2 cans of stewed tomato 
7. 2 8 oz cans of tomato sauce 
8. 1 cup onions 
9. 2 garlic cloves 
10. 1 cup celery 
11. 1 cup carrots 
12. 1 cup mushrooms 
13. 2 cups zucchini 
14. 1 red or green bell pepper 
15. 1/2 tbsp basil 
16. 1/2 tbsp oregano 
17. 3 tbsp parsley 
And don’t forget to add cheese! I added mozzarella but Parmesan is also fantastic!!! 

What recipe should I cook next?!?!
